    <j.0:dossier_title xml:lang="en">Proposal for a COUNCIL DECISION on the position to be taken on behalf of the European Union in the Committee on Trade and Sustainable Development established under the Agreement between the European Union and Japan for an Economic Partnership as regards the adoption of the List of Experts, and the Rules of Procedure for the panel to be convened to examine the matter concerning the interpretation or application of the relevant Articles of Chapter 16</j.0:dossier_title>
